text: SAAZ (СААЗ) (Skopinskiy Avtoagregatniy Zavod, Скопинский Автоагрегатный Завод, SAAZ Complect, СААЗ Комплект) is a Russian factory of automotive components (telescopic struts, shock absorbers, pneumatic-stops and gas springs). The company was established in 1962 and is a supplier of products for conveyors of AvtoVAZ, UAZ and others.
